org.gvsig.raster.impl.store

Interface QueryableRaster

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRasterDataStore, DefaultRasterStore, DefaultRemoteRasterStore

    public interface QueryableRaster
    A kind of dataset which can be queried should implement this interface.
